graph TD
    Start[节点 N 持初始偏好 v] --> Sample[随机抽样 k=20 邻居]
    Sample --> Vote{收到 ≥α 同意 v'？}
    Vote -->|是, v'≠v| Switch[切换偏好为 v']
    Vote -->|是, v'=v| Inc[confidence += 1]
    Vote -->|否| Reset[confidence = 0]
    Inc --> Check{confidence ≥ β？}
    Check -->|是| Decide[决定 v']
    Check -->|否| Sample
    Switch --> Sample
    Reset --> Sample